      <section id="id1170991789600">
        <title>To learn to use the Past Tense correctly [LO 6.2.6]</title>
        <para id="id2733558">Tense</para>
        <para id="id8304435">Verbs change their form to show time (tense) when an action is done.</para>
        <para id="id2544401">There are three Tenses:</para>
        <para id="id1170989746344"><emphasis effect="bold">1. PRESENT TENSE </emphasis>(The action is being done now.)</para>
        <para id="id4990219">I write</para>
        <para id="id5491277">I am writing</para>
        <para id="id2561984"><emphasis effect="bold">2. PAST TENSE </emphasis>(The action has been done.)</para>
        <para id="id8183506">I wrote</para>
        <para id="id1170991647580">I was writing</para>
        <para id="id2574418"><emphasis effect="bold">3. FUTURE TENSE </emphasis>(The action will take place in the future)</para>
        <para id="id3017708">I shall write</para>
        <para id="id8626370">He will write</para>
        <para id="id1170981511668">Write out the sentences below in the past tense:</para>
        <list id="id1170982925570" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
          <item>Billy Wonks jumps up and down.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id8142296"/>
        <para id="id8792280"/>
        <list id="id1170988424120" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
          <item>Charles finds the fifth golden ticket.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id1170988213499"/>
        <para id="id7430149"/>
        <list id="id7354453" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
          <item>The Oupa-Looms sing a merry song.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id1170988540382"/>
        <para id="id3647328"/>
        <list id="id8143368" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
          <item>The rhododendron’s blossoms are pink, nave and red.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id5877668"/>
        <para id="id6921329"/>
        <list id="id7207271" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
          <item>Miss Gobblegum chews bubble-gum all the time.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id7682957"/>
        <para id="id2824560"/>
        <para id="id1170988568899"/>
        <list id="id6936092" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
          <item>Violet screams with fright.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id1170991704255"/>
        <para id="id1170989799252"/>
        <list id="id2762753" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
          <item>The delicious chocolates satisfy the children.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id1170984203629"/>
        <para id="id7229978"/>
        <list id="id6149055" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
          <item>Grandpa smokes a pipe.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id3516597"/>
        <para id="id6943317"/>
        <list id="id8303407" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
          <item>They never fight or kick or punch.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id6916827"/>
        <para id="id5270489"/>
        <list id="id1170984076432" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
          <item>They leave you free to cook the lunch.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id3678451"/>
        <para id="id7383301"/>
